    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-08-24T00:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-08-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="864"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d864">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.42793/8–2444: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gauss</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Chungking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-08-24T12:00:00+07:00"
                            >August 24, 1944—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received 1:10 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1450. High official of Ministry of Education states privately that ban on private
                    students to the United States soon to be lifted; that 1200 students would
                    proceed to the United States in autumn after further local training; that
                    maximum of 30% of these would be members of Kuomintang or San Min Chu I Youth
                    Corps; and that no efforts would be made to control [thought?] while in United
                    States (Embassy’s No. 1371, August 9, 1 p.m.<note n="44" xml:id="d864fn44">Not
                        printed.</note>) Official made no mention of how transportation is to be
                    arranged. Acute surface transportation problem from India apparently
                    unchanged.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gauss</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
